OL,3,CPost Office Inquiry: Horizon scandal
OL,4,Cdrove 13 people to suicide, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FA damning report into the Post Office
OL,8,FHorizon IT scandal has concluded at
OL,9,Fleast 13 people may have taken their
OL,10,Fown lives after being accused of
OL,11,Fwrongdoing.
OL,13,FThe report, issued as part of the long-
OL,14,Frunning inquiry into the faulty
OL,15,FHorizon IT system used in Post Office
OL,16,Fbranches, described the impact on
OL,17,Fsubpostmasters as "disastrous" and
OL,18,Fsaid it heard evidence from 59 others
OL,19,Fwho had also contemplated suicide as a
OL,20,Fresult of the pressures from the
OL,21,Fscandal.
