OL,3,CPost Office Inquiry: Horizon scandal
OL,4,Cdrove 13 people to suicide, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FApproximately 1,000 subpostmasters
OL,8,Fwere wrongfully prosecuted by the Post
OL,9,FOffice between 1999 and 2015 after the
OL,10,Ffaulty Legacy Horizon software made it
OL,11,Flook as though money was missing from
OL,12,Ftheir accounts.
OL,14,FTuesday's 162-page report, written by
OL,15,Finquiry chair Sir Wyn Williams, also
OL,16,Fconcluded Post Office bosses knew the
OL,17,FHorizon IT system had widespread
OL,18,Ffaults, but had "maintained the
OL,19,Ffiction" it was accurate for years.
