OL,3,CPost Office Inquiry: Horizon scandal
OL,4,Cdrove 13 people to suicide, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FSir Wyn said: "Although many of the
OL,8,Findividuals who gave evidence before
OL,9,Fme were very reluctant to accept it I
OL,10,Fam satisfied from the evidence that I
OL,11,Fhave heard that a number of senior, or
OL,12,Fnot so senior employees, of the Post
OL,13,FOffice knew or at the very least
OL,14,Fshould have known that Legacy Horizon
OL,15,Fwas capable of error.
OL,17,F"Yet, for all practical purposes,
OL,18,Fthroughout the lifetime of Legacy
OL,19,FHorizon, the Post Office maintained
OL,20,Fthe fiction that its data was always
OL,21,Faccurate".
