OL,3,CPost Office Inquiry: Horizon scandal
OL,4,Cdrove 13 people to suicide, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe report continued by examining the
OL,8,Finsufficiencies of the government's
OL,9,Ffour compensation schemes: the Horizon
OL,10,FShortfall Scheme (HSS), the Group
OL,11,FLitigation Order (GLO) Scheme, the
OL,12,FOverturned Convictions (OC) scheme,
OL,13,Fand the Horizon Convictions Redress
OL,14,FScheme (HCRS).
OL,16,F"In my view, the Post Office, the
OL,17,FDepartment and Ministers simply failed
OL,18,Fto grasp how difficult it would be to
OL,19,Fprovide financial redress in a timely
OL,20,Ffashion to all those who were or would
OL,21,Fvery likely become eligible," he wrote.
