OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FHe singled out the government's
OL,8,Frefusal to provide funded legal advice
OL,9,Funder the HSS scheme - despite it
OL,10,Fbeing available under all other
OL,11,Fcompensation routes.
OL,13,F"The department continues to resist
OL,14,Fthis as if its life depended on
OL,15,Fit...in my view, the department's
OL,16,Fstance on this issue is indefensible,"
OL,17,Fhe wrote.
