OL,3,CPost Office Inquiry: Horizon scandal
OL,4,Cdrove 13 people to suicide, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FDespite government efforts to deliver
OL,8,Fcompensation, hundreds of
OL,9,Fsubpostmasters are still waiting, some
OL,10,Fmore than two decades after they were
OL,11,Fwrongly accused.
OL,13,FIt clarifies that compensation awarded
OL,14,Fto the victims of the scandal should
OL,15,Fbe the equivalent of what would be
OL,16,Freceived at the "top end of the
OL,17,Fappropriate range of damages," which
OL,18,Fthey would receive in court.
