OL,4,Cdrove 13 people to suicide, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe report also asked the government
OL,8,Fto establish a standing public body
OL,9,Fthat would oversee financial redress
OL,10,Fto people who have been wronged by
OL,11,Fpublic bodies in the future.
OL,13,FIt also called on the government to
OL,14,Fcreate a formal process for providing
OL,15,Ffinancial redress to the close family
OL,16,Fmembers of those most adversely
OL,17,Faffected by the Horizon scandal.
